(91, 1, '2022-11-18 03:30:56', '2022-11-18 03:30:56', '<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Contact</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><br>Les 2 meilleures façons de nous rejoindre sont sur Facebook ou par courriel.<br><br>Pour la boutique en ligne, veuillez adresser vos messages à la boutique de Montréal ou Brossard.<br><br></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center\">Montréal - Plateau Mont-Royal (Coin St-Denis et Mont-Royal)<br><br>514-543-7311</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:contact-form-7/contact-form-selector -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-contact-form-7-contact-form-selector\">[contact-form-7 id=\"84\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]</div>\n<!-- /wp:contact-form-7/contact-form-selector -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":55,\"width\":-152,\"height\":-152,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized is-style-default\"><img src=\"http://localhost/laLicornerie-LesLicornesGonflables/wordpress/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/1-sirop_rose.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-55\" width=\"-152\" height=\"-152\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>408 Avenue du Mont-Royal Est,<br><br>Montréal (Québec) H2J 1W1</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>À moins d’une minute à pied de la Station Mont-Royal.<br><br>Autobus 11, 30, 97 et 427 passent à moins d’une minute à pied. Les autobus 14 et 55 passent à environ 10 minutes à pied.<br><br>Le REV St-Denis passe juste sous notre terrasse rue St-Denis<br><br>Stationnement disponible sur la rue St-Denis (à l’année) et sur Mont-Royal (d’octobre à mai).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-11-18 03:30:56', '2022-11-18 03:30:56', '', 20, 'http://localhost/laLicornerie-LesLicornesGonflables/wordpress/wordpress/?p=91', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(92, 1, '2022-11-18 20:18:14', '2022-11-18 20:18:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>Accueil</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\" />\n\n  <link href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"\n    integrity=\"sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" />\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\"\n    integrity=\"sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM\"\n    crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@8/swiper-bundle.min.css\" />\n\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@8/swiper-bundle.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <nav class=\"navbar navbar-light navbar-expand-lg\">\n      <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"index.html\"><img class=\"header__logo__img\" src=\"assets/logo.png\"\n          alt=\"imgage licorne rainbow\" />\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <button class=\"navbar-toggler\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mainNav\" aria-controls=\"mainNav\"\n          aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Affichage/masquage de la navigation\">\n          <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n        </button>\n\n        <div id=\"mainNav\" class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\">\n          <ul class=\"navbar-nav\">\n            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n              <a href=\"page_boutique/boutique.html\" class=\"nav-link\">Boutique</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n              <a href=\"/page_evenement/evenement.html\" class=\"nav-link\">Évènements</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n              <a href=\"page-2.html\" class=\"nav-link\">Contact</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n              <a href=\"pages/page_nouvelle/nouvelle.html\" class=\"nav-link\">Nouvelles</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"nav-item\">\n              <form>\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"text\" class=\"navbar__recherche\" placeholder=\"Recherche\" />\n                <button class=\"my-button\" aria-label=\"Smile\"></button>\n              </form>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </nav>\n  </header>\n\n  <main>\n    <section class=\"main-hero\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n          <div class=\"col-6\">\n            <h1>La Licornerie</h1>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n          <div class=\"col-6\">\n            <div class=\"hero-swiper\">\n              <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                  <img class=\"header-img\" src=\"../medias/boutique/13-kevin_2.jpg\" alt=\"logo\" />\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                  <img class=\"header-img\" src=\"../medias/boutique/13-kevin.jpg\" alt=\"logo\" />\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                  <img class=\"header-img\" src=\"../medias/boutique/13-kevin_3.jpg\" alt=\"logo\" />\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"hero-swiper-pagination\"></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"main-categorie\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n          <div class=\"col-6\">\n            <H2>Magasinez Par Catégories</H2>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"categorie-swiper\">\n              <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                  <img class=\"cercle\" src=\"../medias/boutique/1-sirop_emeraude.png\" alt=\"logo\" />\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                  <img class=\"cercle\" src=\"../medias/boutique/11-mirroir.jpg\" alt=\"logo\" />\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                  <img class=\"cercle\" src=\"../medias/boutique/4-collier_licorne.jpg\" alt=\"logo\" />\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"categorie-swiper-pagination\"></div>\n              <div class=\"categorie-swiper-button-prev\"></div>\n              <div class=\"categorie-swiper-button-next\"></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"main-vedette\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n          <div class=\"col-12\">\n            <H2>Produits Vedettes</H2>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row\">\n          <div class=\"col-4 vedette\">\n            <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem;\">\n              <img src=\"../medias/boutique/7-unicorn_poop.jpg\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"poop\">\n              <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <h5 class=\"card-title\">item-licorne</h5>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">mini description</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Voir</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col-4 vedette\">\n            <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem;\">\n              <img src=\"../medias/boutique/9-Emma_licorne_sorbet.jpg\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"poop\">\n              <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <h5 class=\"card-title\">item-licorne</h5>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">mini description</p>\n                <a href=\"pages/page_produit/produit.html\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Voir</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col-4 vedette\">\n            <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem;\">\n              <img src=\"../medias/boutique/2-laurie_licorne.jpg\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"poop\">\n              <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <h5 class=\"card-title\">item-licorne</h5>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">mini description</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Voir</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row\">\n          <div class=\"col-4 vedette\">\n            <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem;\">\n              <img src=\"../medias/boutique/12-thermos.jpg\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"poop\">\n              <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <h5 class=\"card-title\">item-licorne</h5>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">mini description</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Voir</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col-4 vedette\">\n            <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem;\">\n              <img src=\"../medias/boutique/1-sirop_licorne.jpg\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"poop\">\n              <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <h5 class=\"card-title\">item-licorne</h5>\n                <p class=\"card-text\">mini description</p>\n                <a href=\"page_produit/produit.html\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Voir</a>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col-4 vedette\">\n            <div class=\"card\" style=\"width: 18rem;\">\n              <img src=\"../medias/boutique/15-meowchi.jpg\" class=\"card-img-top\" alt=\"poop\">\n              <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <h5 class=\"card-t